        "timestamp": "2019-03-26 17:34:02.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\n> If you add the following to the script KEY_STORE_PASSWORD=\"${KEY_STORE_PASSWORD:-\\\"\\\"}\"\n > (following the same pattern as APP_HOME) then you will ensure that\n > a default password value of an empty string is passed to the\n > Application\n\nThere is no need for us to set the default to empty string. For POMBA deployment $KEY_STORE_PASSWORD will be configured from the Chart. Please merge, thanks!",
